magelo will be in soon....</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uskewert.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Skewert</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/6/02 1:45:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11731.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: huh?</span><hr size=1> First off, the +2 disease damage is NOT just an extra 2hp's of damage on the mob.  It is added to the base damage of the weapon, and calculated as if that weapon was, in this case, a 12 dmg weapon.<br>
